Blue node degrees in this interpretation

n0, n1, n2, n3, n4 have degree 4 from the rooted tree.
Each leaf nX.Y has degree 4 total: one tree edge to its parent and two edges to
one outer connector on each of its two red connections.
Each outer connector oK has degree 2.

